00:01:50.343 --> 00:01:51.445 align:middle line:90%
No sense. Yeah.

00:01:51.445 --> 00:01:52.780 align:middle line:84%
And I'll never forget
when I first started

00:01:52.780 --> 00:01:54.548 align:middle line:90%
to study precious metals.

00:01:54.548 --> 00:01:57.384 align:middle line:84%
